                    <p align=justify>It looks like <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bitcoin">BitCoin</a> is getting huge popularity nowadays. This virtual currency is now traded at around $970 per 1 BTC. I'm experimenting with bitcoins myself too. Do you have some spare bitcoins? Are you willing to donate a fraction of BTC? If so, I will be very grateful so I could experiment more :)</p><p>
