                    <h2><a href="/en/blog/22395-Slax-update.html" style="color: #333333;">Slax update</a></h2>
                    <p align=justify>I tried to make another Slax update, following the progress of KDE, Xorg and other software, but I got some issues again with KDE's task bar not being drawn properly. I have to admit that this drives me crazy :) So I guess it will be better to wait for another KDE update.<div class="bottom50"><i class="icon-user"></i> <a href="/en/blog/22395-Slax-update.html#comments">21 comments</a>&nbsp; <i class="icon-eye-open"></i> <a href="/en/blog/22395-Slax-update.html#firstnew">21 new</a></div>
