                    <h2><a href="/en/blog/22169-Diffbundle-from-7.0.6-to-7.0.8-updated-.html" style="color: #333333;">Diffbundle from 7.0.6 to 7.0.8 (updated)</a></h2>
                    <p align=justify><div class="alert alert-success">UPDATE - so it is confirmed, 7.0.7 didn't fully fix the plasma panel, so 7.0.8 is on its way. Diffbundle available here:</b> <a href="http://www.slax.org/upload/99-diff-706-708.sb">http://www.slax.org/upload/99-diff-706-708.sb</a></div></p><p>
